snippet.title: Resident Evil - Raccoon City Incident Report
snippet.description:
What really happened in Raccoon City? If you need a quick recap of the RE storyline before Resident Evil 3 launches on April 3rd, we've got you covered!

For more official news and updates, follow us on:

Visit www.residentevil.com for more information.
